1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,400
What if 10,000 hours of practice isn’t the key to expertise?

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:10,400
The popular myth claims mastery comes from sheer repetition, but science paints a different picture.

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:15,200
Studies show quality of practice matters more than quantity—think deliberate, focused efforts.

4
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,200
Experts recommend feedback and reflection over mindless hours spent grinding.

5
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:22,800
So, don’t just count the hours—make each one meaningful.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,200
That’s the real secret to mastery.

7
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:27,600
Curious about more myths in learning?

